Link: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HcM_apiZZ7c

Definition:
SAP LSMW stands for SAP Legacy System Migration Workbench. This tool primarily use to transfer data from external system/legacy system to SAP system.

Implememtation:
1. Go to LSMW T-CODE.
2. Provide PROJECT NAME, SUB-PROJECT and OBJECT
3. Click DEFINE OBJEVCT ATTRIBUTES.  Select BATCH INPUT RECORDING and provide RECORDING NAME. Then click CREATE  ICON. Provide CREATE RECORDING details and T-CODE
